# Reports (RU locale)

One JSON + one chat report per phase. No `*_brief.md`.

Chat reports are written in **Russian** — the product owner reads them. Rules, skills, code, and JSON keys stay English.

| Phase | Chat header |
|-------|-------------|
| layout | ОТЧЁТ: РАЗМЕТКА |
| plan | ОТЧЁТ: ПЛАН |
| build | ОТЧЁТ: СБОРКА |
| inspect | ОТЧЁТ: ОСМОТР |
| debug | ОТЧЁТ: ТРИАЖ |
| fix | ОТЧЁТ: ПОЧИНКА |
| autobuild | ОТЧЁТ: АВТОСБОРКА |
| autofix | ОТЧЁТ: АВТОПОЧИНКА |
| batch | ОТЧЁТ: ПАКЕТ |

Clarification block: `УТОЧНЕНИЕ (layout|inspect)` + concrete questions in Russian — region/node, 2–3 options, what is blocked.

Every report ends with a `Check:` line quoting `check.mjs` result (`0 failures` or the failing lines).

JSON keys and `figma_id` values — as-is (English). Prose values in JSON (`screen_summary`, `symptom`, contract statements, …) — Russian.
